#: inc/class-wpseo-replace-vars.php:110
msgid "A replacement variable can not start with \"%%cf_\" or \"%%ct_\" as these are reserved for the WPSEO standard variable variables for custom fields and custom taxonomies. Try making your variable name unique."
msgstr "ຕົວແປແທນບໍ່ສາມາດເລີ່ມຕົ້ນດ້ວຍ \"%%cf_\" ຫຼື \"%%ct_\" ເນື່ອງຈາກຖືກສະຫງວນໄວ້ສຳລັບຕົວແປມາດຕະຖານຂອງ WPSEO. ກະລຸນາຕັ້ງຊື່ຕົວແປໃຫ້ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ."

#: inc/class-wpseo-replace-vars.php:107
msgid "A replacement variable can only contain alphanumeric characters, an underscore or a dash. Try renaming your variable."
msgstr "ຕົວແປແທນສາມາດມີໄດ້ສະເພາະຕົວເລກ, ຕົວອັກສອນພາສາອັງກິດ, ຂີດກາງ ຫຼື ຂີດກ້ອງເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

